dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Terry Long. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Michelle. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six seven eight nine and my date of birth is zero five dash one two dash one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Michelle. One last piece of information needed, could you confirm your current address for our records, please?
Of course, my address is one two three Main Street, Cityville, State, one zero zero zero one.
Thank you for providing that information, Michelle. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now, thank you.
Great! Thank you for your time, Michelle. Have a wonderful day!
